news.headline: Bitcoin Price Hits Fresh Record. How Fed Could Hamper Crypto.
news.summary: Bitcoin  price hit an all-time high of more than $106,000 early Monday, reaping further gains from President-elect Donald Trump’s plans to deregulate cryptos and create a national strategic reserve of bitcoin.  The slight drop could be due to fears the Federal Reserve will adopt a more hawkish tone

news.headline: It's All About The Fed Now
news.summary: Despite potential near-term volatility and pullbacks, the SPX remains in a constructive uptrend, with a 2025 year-end target of around 7,000. Read the full market outlook on Seeking Alpha.

news.headline: The Santa Claus Rally Under Attack
news.summary: Last week, the market's Santa Claus rally came under attack by the bond bears. Given participation in the stock market by American households is at an all-time high, there's a lot at stake.
